This file describes the changes to the Log for C++ library. See the CVS repository for more detailed descriptions.

2000/12/07 0.1: 
Added Doxygen generated API documentation. Most of it has been copied verbatim from LOG4J.
Added NDC (Nested Diagnostic Context) class.
Added OstreamAppender.
Added SyslogAppender.
Fixed bug in HierarchyMaintainer: getInstance should NOT set the Appender of a
newly instantiated Category.                
                
